'''2015年10月乍得炸彈襲擊'''，是指2015年10月10日一連串發生在[[乍得|乍得]]的炸彈襲擊，懷疑由[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]組織[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]所為。

== 過程 ==
巴加索拉是一條位於乍得西部的村落，大量[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]人因{{link-en|博科聖地在尼日利亞的叛亂|Boko Haram insurgency}}而逃難到此村落；2015年10月10日，一群女性襲擊者在巴加索拉的市場發動[[自殺式炸彈襲擊|自殺式炸彈襲擊]]<ref name=harm>{{cite news |title=Suspected Boko Haram suicide bombers kill at least 36 in Chad |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/suicide-bombings-chad-1.3266518 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |agency=The Associated Press |date=2015-10-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151014055631/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/suicide-bombings-chad-1.3266518 |archivedate=2015-10-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。事發的市場是一所繁忙的{{link-en|魚市場|Fish market}}，有目擊者表示只聽到一聲爆炸<ref name=heard>{{cite news |title=Lake Chad's Baga Sola town hit by suicide bombers |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-34498417 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |agency=BBC |date=2015-10-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011000836/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-34498417 |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>；當地警方發言人則表示，市場內共發生了三次爆炸<ref name=three>{{cite news |title=5 suicide bombings target Chad, killing at least 36 people |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/ap/article-3267746/Suicide-bombings-Chad-market-refugee-camp-kill-38.html |accessdate=2015-10-16 |agency=ASSOCIATED PRESS |date=2015-10-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151016055152/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/ap/article-3267746/Suicide-bombings-Chad-market-refugee-camp-kill-38.html |archivedate=2015-10-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。這次是巴加索拉首次遭到如此襲擊<ref>{{cite news |title=41 killed in Lake Chad blasts blamed on Boko Haram |url=http://www.rappler.com/world/regions/africa/108918-lake-chad-blasts-boko-haram |accessdate=2015-10-15 |agency=Agence France-Presse |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151015055723/http://www.rappler.com/world/regions/africa/108918-lake-chad-blasts-boko-haram |archivedate=2015-10-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。其後，位置接近上述市場、容納了超過3,000名[[難民|難民]]的達累斯薩拉姆難民營附近亦發生了兩次自殺式炸彈襲擊<ref name=three/>。

發動是次炸彈襲擊的自殺式襲擊者共有五人，其中有兩名兒童<ref name=three/>；乍得當局懷疑是次襲擊由博科聖地發動，該組織在2015年6月亦曾在乍得首都[[恩賈梅納|恩賈梅納]]進行了一次自殺式襲擊<ref name=heard/>。截至2015年10月15日，襲擊共造成41人死亡<ref>{{cite news |title=Schoolgirl kidnapped by Boko Haram 'reveals horrors faced by captives' |url=http://uk.onlinenigeria.com/latest-additions/181358-schoolgirl-kidnapped-by-boko-haram-reveals-horrors-faced-by-captives.html |accessdate=2015-10-16 |agency=UK Nigeria Online |date=2015-10-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151016090710/http://uk.onlinenigeria.com/latest-additions/181358-schoolgirl-kidnapped-by-boko-haram-reveals-horrors-faced-by-captives.html |archivedate=2015-10-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；是次襲擊的傷者數字出現矛盾，乍得政府聲稱有48名傷者，[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]則指有53人在此襲擊中受傷（其中14人為兒童）<ref name=harm/>。

== 反應 ==
[[非洲聯盟委員會|非洲聯盟委員會]]主席[[恩科薩扎娜·德拉米尼-祖馬|恩科薩扎娜·德拉米尼-祖馬]]強烈譴責是次恐怖襲擊和博科聖地翌日在[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]發動的另一宗襲擊，批評此兩宗襲擊是野蠻的行徑，對受害者家屬表示哀悼，又祝願傷者早日康復<ref>{{cite web |title=The African Union strongly condemns the Boko Haram terrorist attacks in Chad and Cameroon |url=http://www.peaceau.org/en/article/the-african-union-strongly-condemns-the-boko-haram-terrorist-attacks-in-chad-and-cameroon |website=African Union Peace and Security Department |accessdate=2015-10-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151016055532/http://www.peaceau.org/en/article/the-african-union-strongly-condemns-the-boko-haram-terrorist-attacks-in-chad-and-cameroon |archivedate=2015-10-16 |deadurl=no |date=2015-10-12 }}</ref>。[[聯合國難民署|聯合國難民署]]亦對此襲擊作出譴責<ref>{{cite news |author1=Lisa Schlein |title=UNHCR Condemns Deadly Boko Haram Attacks in Chad |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/unhcr-condemns-deadly-boko-haram-suicide-attacks-in-lake-chad-region/3003947.html |accessdate=2015-10-16 |agency=VOANews.com |date=2015-10-13 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151014055548/http://www.voanews.com/content/unhcr-condemns-deadly-boko-haram-suicide-attacks-in-lake-chad-region/3003947.html |archivedate=2015-10-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

